# Integration first (settings & CRUD)

- **Integration (`*.integration.test.ts`)** — server actions, services, repos, toggles, auth, pantry switch. Must catch regressions (e.g. settings toggle + `bindSubmitting` / `syncFormData` + PGlite persistence).
- **E2E** — few critical journeys only (register/login → hem, scan hub, receipt smoke, settings page loads). Do **not** add reload/toggle persistence E2E for settings.
- New settings or household behavior: extend `settings.integration.test.ts`, `pantry-actions.integration.test.ts`, or domain service integration — not Playwright detail tests.
